  "texts": [
    "As such, we conduct an extensive inference time hyperparameter search aimed at minimizing error propagation.",
    "From the joint contributions of our cascaded simultaneous translation system and minimization of error propagation, we achieve impressive results on the ACL 60/60 development set.",
    "For example, on the English→German language pair, our cascaded system achieves a BLEU of 24.64 and 27.83 at a streamLAAL of 1837.86 and 3343.73.",
    "Furthermore, on the English→Chinese task, our system achieves a BLEU of 34.07 and 37.23 at a streamLAAL of 2216.99 and 3521.35.",
    "Simultaneous translation, generally speaking, is the process of taking in some source context and making translation decisions to another language in a manner that does not rely on that source context being complete."
  ],
